.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: red, green, ivory, yellow, blue
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: skateboarding, soccer, basketball, tennis, sailing
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-gold, kools, chesterfields, lucky-strike, parliaments
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea, milk, orange-juice, water
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: punk, rock, folk, classical, jazz

1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person who likes red
2. the person who's sport is soccer is the fan of punk
3. the person drinking coffee is the person who likes green
4. the person who's sport is basketball is the person drinking tea
5. the person who likes green is to the right of the person who likes ivory
6. the old-gold-smoker is the fan of jazz
7. the kools-smoker is the person who likes yellow
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far left
10. the chesterfields-smoker is on the left or right of the fan of rock
11. the kools-smoker is to the left or right of the fan of classical
12. the lucky-strike-smoker is the person drinking orange-juice
13. the person who's sport is sailing is the parliaments-smoker
14. the person who's sport is tennis is to the left or right of the person who likes blue

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Sport	|   tennis	|    basketball	|     skateboarding	|    soccer	|    sailing	|
| Color		|    yellow	|      blue	|      red	|     ivory	|     green	|
| Beverage	|     water	|      tea	|      milk	| orange-juice	|     coffee	|
| Cigar		|     kools	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| lucky-strike	|   parliament	|
| Music-Genre		|     rock	|     classical	|     jazz	|     punk	|     folk	|
